# Bayesian ETAS Simulation â€” R Markdown Project (Knit Result)

This repository hosts a knitted **R Markdown** (Rmd) report with figures embedded in the PDF. It demonstrates a Bayesian ETAS (Epidemic-Type Aftershock Sequence) simulation and model fitting workflow.

